title: Steve Wilkos You're Busted
description:
YOU'RE BUSTED:
--------------

     Hope lost? 15-year-old Hope grew up without a caring mother and a stable family, bouncing from foster homes, to group homes, to incarceration. Now on the streets, using drugs, and prostituting to survive, Hope's essentially given up on life, and even attempted suicide. Her mother Tanya, now clean and sober, prays it's not too late to save her daughter's life. Sounds like a tragic tale, but could it all just be a lie? Steve knows how to smell a lie, and no one's getting one by him!
